elements.contents: ... that Lesley Akyaa Opoku Ware (pictured), daughter of Asante ruler Opoku Ware II, simultaneously served as Ghana's ambassador to six countries?

elements.title: White River
elements.contents: ... that there are three hydroelectric generating stations on the White River in Northern Ontario, Canada, all part-owned by First Nations?

elements.title: Jane Ingham
elements.contents: ... that the English botanists Jane Ingham and Joseph Hubert Priestley were the first to separate cell walls from meristematic tissues in broad beans?

elements.title: KMXO
